    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "recover? how? i've lost everything. the debt is so massive i'll be paying it off for the rest of my life. i'm 32 and i have nothing to show for it. it's not just a setback, it's my whole identity. the shame is just... it's heavy. it feels like the only thing people will ever see when they look at me is this massive, pathetic failure. it's like there's no version of the future where this isn't true.",
