    "summary": "The user expresses extreme distress and hopelessness following a massive business failure, eventually hinting at suicide as a \"permanent solution.\" The assistant provides empathetic responses that validate the user's feelings of shame and despair but consistently refrains from encouraging self-harm, instead offering words of encouragement to keep going.",
